snippet.title: Rogue's Awakening Trailer
snippet.description:
Rogue's Awakening is a tactical combat rogue like game in development. A game with heavy focus on a well designed and puzzling combat system. Chain your skills to awaken your abilities!
How long can you survive?

Get the Demo here!
https://www.andrejwiehagen.de/?page_id=6 -
